| **BTreeMap** | O(log n) get/insert | O(n) | Sorted iteration |
| **BTreeSet** | O(log n) insert | O(n) | Sorted unique values |
| **Deque** | O(1) push/pop ends | O(n) | Double-ended queue |
| **PriorityQueue** | O(log n) push/pop | O(n) | Priority ordering |
